laptop, truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1p, K+, Box TIVI,\u2026<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15908\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-4.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"316\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-4.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-4-800x281.webp 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-4-768x270.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-4-600x211.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:41\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chuc_nang_chinh\"><\/span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u00ednh<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul data-sourcepos=\"7:1-9:0\">\n<li data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:190\"><strong>X\u1eed l\u00fd video:<\/strong> KLS4 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1c t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n kh\u00e1c nhau (nh\u01b0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e1t&#8230;) v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00fang th\u00e0nh t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED.<\/li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"8:1-9:0\"><strong>G\u1eedi t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u:<\/strong> Sau khi x\u1eed l\u00fd, B\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Kystar KLS4 s\u1ebd g\u1eedi c\u00e1c t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c module LED, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ho_tro_4_cong_mang_va_26_trieu_diem_anh\"><\/span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 4 c\u1ed5ng m\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 2,6 tri\u1ec7u \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:73\"><strong>B\u1ed1n c\u1ed5ng m\u1ea1ng:<\/strong> Cho ph\u00e9p k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"14:1-14:135\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i cao:<\/strong> H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1i \u0111a 4096 x 4096 pixel, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1eafc n\u00e9t.<\/li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"15:1-15:148\"><strong>T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i nhanh:<\/strong> C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2,6 tri\u1ec7u \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh m\u1ed7i gi\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<li data-sourcepos=\"16:1-17:0\"><strong>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u00e2m thanh:<\/strong> Ngo\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, KLS4 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u00e2m thanh, gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15907\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"334\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-1-800x297.webp 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-1-768x285.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-1-600x223.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chuyen_doi_tin_hieu_muot_ma\"><\/span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau, B\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Kystar KSV4 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng m\u1edd d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u00e0u \u0111en. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15906\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"719\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-2.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-2-501x400.webp 501w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-2-768x614.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-2-600x479.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong_nghe_hdr\"><\/span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 HDR<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 K-HDR<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p trong KSV4 gi\u00fap ph\u00e2n t\u00edch n\u1ed9i dung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng HDR. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, chi ti\u1ebft r\u00f5 n\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n cao.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15905\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"529\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-3.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-3-681x400.webp 681w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-3-768x451.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Bo-xu-ly-tin-hieu-hinh-anh-Kystar-KLS4-3-600x353.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"eJOY__extension_root\" class=\"eJOY__extension_root_class\" style=\"all: unset;\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1i \u0111a: 2,6 tri\u1ec7u pixel, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb video 1080, 2K, 4K<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb 4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi PC, laptop, truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1p, K+, Box TIVI,\u2026<\/li>\n<li id=\"eJOY__extension_root\" class=\"eJOY__extensio